{
  "stem": "3973.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was an idea of walking sort of around, so there were some ledges, without dropping the stone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you dropped the stone, you were dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People who dropped the stone, there was one-- they had one particular-- on the top [INAUDIBLE] there was a-- a sharp drop.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The prisoners gave it the name, the parachuter's wall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What they would do is just push you over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So people were dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, and there we had to carry the stones, maybe a mile and a half, two miles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then run back and start over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was their test of who's gonna survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One day, we had a assembly in front of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some German kapos came by, I mean kapos with the prisoners, and look people over, marked down the numbers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the next day they came back and called people by their number.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was one of them called.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was telling this to my brother, we were together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we were separated, were taken out of the camp to another camp-- another barrack, rather.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As it turned out there were only young boys, good looking boys they selected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember there were five or six.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So the first day we stayed in the barracks, all of us, and-- cleaning the windows or washing, stuff like this, [INAUDIBLE] soft spot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But the next day, they took four [? they ?] left behind and two of us was sent back to the stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "As it turned out, I mean, many of the block leaders and the kapos and so on were homosexuals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they picked their victims this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Fortunately, I wasn't-- I didn't meet their standards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the stone quarries.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
